PaginatedResponse.description:
Generic paginated response wrapper for list endpoints.

Contains the requested data items and pagination metadata for fetching additional pages.

Example:
    ```json
    {
        "data": [
            {"order_id": "abc123", "status": "FILLED"},
            {"order_id": "def456", "status": "OPEN"}
        ],
        "pagination": {
            "limit": 100,
            "has_more": true,
            "next_cursor": "1705123456789:def456",
            "total_count": 500
        }
    }
    ```
